import { Card,Typography,Button,CardActionArea,CardMedia,CardContent,CardActions,Box } from "@mui/material"
import { blog1 } from "./BlogImport"





export const Article=({ImgUrl,date,title,button})=>{
    return(
        <>
        <Box>


        <Card sx={{ maxWidth: 500,backgroundColor:'#031B34' }}>
      <CardActionArea>
        <CardMedia
          component="img"
          height="300"
          image={ImgUrl}
          alt="green iguana"
        />
        <CardContent>
          <Typography gutterBottom variant="h6" sx={{color:"white"}}>
              {date}
          </Typography>
          <Typography variant="body2">
            {title}
          </Typography>
        </CardContent>
      </CardActionArea>
      <CardActions>
        <Button size="small" color="primary">
          {button}
        </Button>
      </CardActions>
    </Card>
    </Box>

        </>
    )
}
